To avoid this, use an iterator, and make sure `list` is assigned an `ArrayList`.

```java
Iterator&lt;String&gt; iterator = list.iterator();
while (iterator.hasNext()) {
    if (!StringUtils.isAlphanumeric(iterator.next()))
        iterator.remove();
}
```

